summary: I still haven’t seen Captain Marvel bc I’m Poor (gotta wait for it to come out on streaming), but something just occurred to...
body:
I still haven’t seen Captain Marvel bc I’m Poor (gotta wait for it to come out on streaming), but something just occurred to me.

Everyone talks about how Maria Rambeau and Carol are Extremely Married – I just saw a piece of fanart with Monica climbing on Carol and Carol giving her such a Mom Look™️.

And then I remembered that one of Monica’s superhero names was Captain Marvel and then I had to go lie down and have Feelings.
